pandas
======

create dataframe from columns
-----------------------------
In [1]: col1 = [1,2,3,4,5]
In [2]: col2 = ['a','b','c','d','e']
In [3]: pd.DataFrame(zip(col1, col2), columns=['col1','col2'])
Out[3]:
   col1 col2
0     1    a
1     2    b
2     3    c
3     4    d
4     5    e

create empty dataframe
----------------------
In [1]: pd.DataFrame(columns=['col1','col2'])
Out[1]: 
Empty DataFrame
Columns: [col1, col2]
Index: []
